<p>
<seg id=1> The three accused Bosnia-Herzegovina men were found guilty of war-crimes by the International Court in Hague, however they announced that their senior officer was not guilty. </seg>
<seg id=2> The International Court ruled that their senior officer was not responsible for what happened in the prison camps in Bosnia-Herzegovina. </seg>
<seg id=3> The three accused were sentenced to limited prison terms for atrocity committed in the prison camps as former prisoners described the horrors they saw there. </seg>
</p>
